The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as gender recognition, scene recognition, and object recognition, which are typically categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques such as active learning and subset selection, which fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
